    "faq": {
      "title": "Frequently Asked Questions",
      "subtitle": "Everything you need to know about Chabaqa - the all-in-one community platform for creators, coaches, and educators. Learn about features, pricing, and how to build and monetize your community.",
      "stillHaveQuestions": "Still have questions about Chabaqa?",
      "contactSupport": "Contact Our Support Team",
      "items": [
        {
          "question": "What makes Chabaqa different from other community platforms?",
          "answer": "Chabaqa is an all-in-one community platform built for creators, coaches, and educators who want to grow and monetize their audience in one place. You can create and sell online courses, run interactive challenges, offer one-on-one coaching, host virtual events, and deliver digital products from a single system."
        },
        {
          "question": "How do I create a community on Chabaqa?",
          "answer": "After signing up at chabaqa.io, click Create New Community, add your community name and description, customize colors, banners, and logo, then publish your invite link. Anyone with the link can join instantly."
        },
        {
          "question": "Is Chabaqa only for creating online courses?",
          "answer": "No. Beyond courses, Chabaqa supports paid challenges, digital products, 1:1 coaching sessions, events, and online meetings, all in one dashboard."
        },
        {
          "question": "How will Chabaqa help me engage with my community?",
          "answer": "Chabaqa includes engagement tools like announcements, feeds, direct messages, and communication automations so you can keep members active and connected."
        },
        {
          "question": "How can users book a 1:1 coaching session on Chabaqa?",
          "answer": "Users open the 1:1 sessions section, choose a time slot from your availability calendar, complete booking, and receive confirmation with a meeting link."
        },
        {
          "question": "What is the difference between Courses and Challenges on Chabaqa?",
          "answer": "Courses are flexible learning resources available over time, while challenges are time-based and highly structured programs designed to maximize engagement and outcomes."
        },
        {
          "question": "How can I create and manage events on Chabaqa?",
          "answer": "You can create online or offline events, sell tickets, manage attendees, and track event performance directly from your community dashboard."
        },
        {
          "question": "How much does Chabaqa cost? What are the pricing plans?",
          "answer": "Chabaqa offers flexible plans for different creator stages, including free trial periods and paid tiers with advanced capabilities."
        },
        {
          "question": "Can I use Chabaqa if I'm based in Tunisia or the MENA region?",
          "answer": "Yes. Chabaqa is designed for creators in Tunisia and across the MENA region, with multilingual support and creator-friendly workflows."
        },
        {
          "question": "How do I monetize my community on Chabaqa?",
          "answer": "You can monetize through paid courses, challenges, coaching sessions, events, and digital products with secure checkout and payout support."
        },
        {
          "question": "Is Chabaqa suitable for coaches, educators, and fitness trainers?",
          "answer": "Yes. Chabaqa is built for coaches, educators, trainers, and creators who need an all-in-one platform to teach, engage, and monetize."
        }
      ]
    },
